/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上海菜係咁濃油架喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n回鍋肉個汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又濃又辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f612ee33dfc06e9db90bbb451f44c08da2c152a","tid":226352,"uid":99585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:15:04.000Z","msg":"好想食清炒蝦仁丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有拷扶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df86881ebffe13368d93b3fc5471270075ab3e22","tid":226352,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得罪講句 好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你識條春咩，菜膽有炆過，醬汁夠色夠油光，根本就係好野。<br />\n睇落靚仔夠青夠白個啲好多都係白烚菜膽淋個汁咋懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f313bf517e1b156e58a944ccbf9ff02476ce58a","tid":226352,"uid":62277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想食清炒蝦仁丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有拷扶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n燻魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鱔糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9968b338b0b2a215d892c8082dbff8ebaf1e393e","tid":226352,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>得罪講句 好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你識條春咩，菜膽有炆過，醬汁夠色夠油光，根本就係好野。<br />\n睇落靚仔夠青夠白個啲好多都係白烚菜膽淋個汁咋懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實呢間野唔多注重賣相<br />\n上枱時,d菜係遮曬肉丸<br />\n我夾開d菜先影,整爛左個頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身應該挺身d,圓d"},{"pid":"937a6edf05e32497d7d11730550898220821c196","tid":226352,"uid":99585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T07:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好想食清炒蝦仁丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有拷扶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n燻魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鱔糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我丫公係上海人，以前探佢果陣成日同佢一齊去上海舖頭到食，但佢宜家唔係到，去食上海餸嘅時候都會諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燻魚，鱔糊，仲有長春麵，小籠包，酒糟丸子佢都成日嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}